This paper deals with the problem of multi-label classification for text using RNN sequence models. The most relevant sub-category is likely to be cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper focuses on text classification. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with image classification, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
